text: Currently MediationZone 9 supports the upgrade of MediationZone 8 DTK (agents) plugins by using config contact support. This section describes the porting methods as well as their limitations. This section includes the following sections: Creating New Config Class Generating New Config Class using DTK Limitations of porting existing DTK agents from Version 8 to Version 9
title: Porting agent configuration from Version 8 DTK - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
